Blackjack by Paul Serra, all rights to this game are currently reserved.
If you would like to use this code for anything other than personal use
email me at Addiction2Code@Gmail.com for rights.

Run the program, the it's pretty straight forward.
At the end of your plays, the game will display your winning ratio.
This can be a good tool to find out if on average you're winning.

* This program uses a virtual deck of cards, so it is pretty accurate.
* The cards are shuffled between each game.

Update are on the way!
